{"tid":1196531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，有冇搞撚錯，c朗拿度又攞多一個國家盃， 我美斯攞個美洲杯都追唔撚切呀","createTime":"2019-06-09T20:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:02:02.000Z","uid":43785,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"218b22636dfdb50c8473911614b0f967bf694004","tid":1196531,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:43:20.000Z","msg":"屌，有冇搞撚錯，<br />\nc朗拿度又攞多一個國家盃， <br />\n我美斯攞個美洲杯都追唔撚切啦。<br />\n<br />\n仲以為今年美洲盃， 其他球隊死嘅死傷嘅傷，阿根廷好大機會贏。<br />\n美斯可以追平c朗拿度歐洲盃紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，依家點撚樣追呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慶幸嘅係c朗拿度贏咗雲迪克， <br />\n雲迪克攞得一個杯咋， <br />\n我個美斯仍然好有機會贏番金球獎。<br />\n希望今年美斯攞埋美洲盃，贏個金球獎返嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f695fcf55629205d1550abb6257872030a54cdec","tid":1196531,"uid":217509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62e8c5a120e88b60c67f7c492921b1d1f8980b87","tid":1196531,"uid":217509,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b751bea3c7173a01fc41e951e2e807277bb36684","tid":1196531,"uid":134997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:45:57.000Z","msg":"美洲杯一星期一次，一年之後已經攞咗53次，驚閪"},{"pid":"94eb077be32e978851b8da34873e42466d3cb9c2","